OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry into the
OL,6,Fevening but thickening cloud and
OL,7,Fstrengthening winds will bring patchy
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain overnight to all
OL,9,Fareas. Chilly, but a frost unlikely
OL,10,Faway from rural areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FOvernight rain clearing
OL,13,Fthrough the morning with winds easing
OL,14,Fsomewhat. Brighter into the day though
OL,15,Foccasional showers are expected and
OL,16,Fremaining breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
